+Kind=Negative|Zero|Positive
*Graph(nodes:U,edges:U)
*Path(cost:U)

>classify(x:I):Kind
  x<0 >> Negative
  x==0 >> Zero
  _ >> Positive

~shortest_path(graph:Graph,start:U,goal:U):Path # TODO: choose Dijkstra or A* and design complexity in Rust
~optimize(path:Path):Path # TODO: optimize the path in Rust

>plan(graph:Graph,start:U,goal:U):Path=
  shortest_path(graph,start,goal)
  /> optimize
